lead_paragraph: Breanna Stewart says top-ranked UConn symbolically turned the calendar to March in the second half Monday, overcoming the team's first halftime deficit in almost a year.

headline.print_headline: UConn Overcomes Halftime Deficit to Beat USF 79-59
